br.otimizes.oplatool.architecture.representation

Class OperationsOverAssociation

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.otimizes.oplatool.architecture.representation.OperationsOverAssociation

  • public class OperationsOverAssociation
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to perform operations on Associations. Its use is made as follows:

    a.forAssociation().createAssociationEnd()
    .withKlass(class1)
    .withMultiplicity("1..*")
    .navigable()
    .and()
    .createAssociationEnd()
    .withKlass(class2)
    .withMultiplicity("1..1)
    .navigable().build();
